{"tid":1464714,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［機場C行］我屌撚曬你地","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:32:06.000Z","uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"174c2b7abd22e8cd7c47611775f47f4384350d96","tid":1464714,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:22:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓下班手足既努力無人睇到喇</span><br />\n<br />\n依家啲藍絲group share C行啲片share得好開心<br />\n諗清楚我地有冇比鬼帶到風向？<br />\n明明95%機場都係和理非努力宣傳<br />\n又令到機場運作出現問題<br />\n但係就比C行啲鬼搶晒所有鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n無人記得721 811<br />\n無人記得還眼<br />\n無人記得五大訴求<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">問清楚自己係咪想要呢啲野</span><br />\n<br />\n諗清楚<br />\n有鬼攪事自己應該點做<br />\n埋去起哄個結果今晚睇到喇<br />\n一定唔係離目標更近<br />\n<br />\n黑警入場<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">又起哄圍埋去？</span><br />\n比鏡頭睇我地唔理性既一面？<br />\n<br />\n明明鬼攪事同黑警入場都係充滿住鏡頭既好時機<br />\n散開啲比記者睇佢地柒咪得囉<br />\n你估佢地個個影帝唔會出錯？<span style=\"color: red;\">老臨黎咋</span><br />\n我地配個background music比live播<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Fight for freedom stay with HK</span><br />\n一睇新聞片就知我地叫五大訴求同班老臨唔係同一班人啦<br />\n<br />\n打死個公安都唔會有五大訴求<br />\n唔比記者同救護做野果啲叫黑警<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">劍指暴政，表達訴求</span></span><br />\n呢啲先係抗爭者呀<br />\n<br />\n利申：P牌，我一日只有一次機會屌醒我地（包括我自己"},{"pid":"7f6f9225762973014440e299c3ee1f56bf36e3e8","tid":1464714,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:23:52.000Z","msg":"［正視聽］大家唔好再嘈啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a60336f48141262fb8afb4f4e1c0aa8219c600d2","tid":1464714,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:24:41.000Z","msg":"巴打絲打們岩睇幫手推<br />\n我P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dcd31d7637d4cde7acc1dfb1d327b20bef91d4e","tid":1464714,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:27:14.000Z","msg":"不割蓆<br />\n不分化<br />\n互相提點<br />\n一次一次進步<br />\n呢啲係咪我地行到呢一步既關鍵呀？"},{"pid":"d33fd84a79976a930b7352eb04e459f79d650211","tid":1464714,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:27:58.000Z","msg":"P牌無人理"},{"pid":"33acb8b5a0e37733abfe05fe626a5a78e3ee9368","tid":1464714,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:28:32.000Z","msg":"重整旗鼓"},{"pid":"1a2406e5cba84ed12e0f65ba5abe0570e8a44e19","tid":1464714,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}